msgctxt "wizard.mixedPrompt.playlistLimit"
msgid "Playlist probe limit: {{count}} items"
msgstr "Kikomo cha kuchunguza playlist: vipengee {{count}}"

msgctxt "wizard.mixedPrompt.playlistTooltip"
msgid "Uses yt-dlp playlist mode and fetches up to your playlist probe limit before showing the picker."
msgstr "Hutumia modi ya playlist ya yt-dlp na kuchukua hadi kikomo chako kabla ya kuonyesha kichaguaji."

msgctxt "wizard.mixedPrompt.quickBody"
msgid "Download only this video, or queue the whole playlist with your active Quick Download profile."
msgstr "Pakua video hii pekee, au ongeza orodha yote ya kucheza kwenye foleni kwa wasifu wako amilifu wa Upakuaji wa haraka."

msgctxt "wizard.mixedPrompt.quickLimitDescription"
msgid "Maximum entries Arroxy scans before queueing a playlist, channel, or search result."
msgstr "Idadi ya juu ya vipengee ambavyo Arroxy hukagua kabla ya kuongeza orodha ya kucheza, kituo au matokeo ya utafutaji kwenye foleni."

msgctxt "wizard.mixedPrompt.quickPlaylistTooltip"
msgid "Queues every loaded playlist item with the active Quick Download profile. If the scan hits your limit, Arroxy asks before queueing."
msgstr "Huongeza kila kipengee cha orodha ya kucheza kilichopakiwa kwenye foleni kwa wasifu amilifu wa Upakuaji wa haraka. Ukaguzi ukifika kikomo chako, Arroxy itauliza kabla ya kuongeza kwenye foleni."

msgctxt "wizard.mixedPrompt.quickSingleTooltip"
msgid "Queues one download and ignores the playlist attached to this URL."
msgstr "Huongeza upakuaji mmoja kwenye foleni na kupuuza orodha ya kucheza iliyoambatishwa kwenye URL hii."

